--- !u!114 &786143717
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 786143716}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0e4f0ee2c5f7cac4eaab656572a8595f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  narrationDatabase:
  - narrationId: nar1
    narrationLines:
    - There lived a man, alone in his world.
    - Standing in curiosity, speaking to the imaginary.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar2a
    narrationLines:
    - /Roses grew/, and the emptiness slowly faded.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar2b
    narrationLines:
    - Everything became much more beautiful.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar3
    narrationLines:
    - As he finished, a strange feeling arrived.
    - A new world, waiting to be /opened/.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar4
    narrationLines:
    - A girl appeared, dressed in red, shimmering in his eyes.
    - Never had he seen a sight quite as beautiful as her.
    - He /tried to draw her near/, welcoming her into his world.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar5
    narrationLines:
    - Every step she took turned the white roses crimson.
    - He fell in love with her magic, a power that painted the pale petals red.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar6
    narrationLines:
    - Once they met, they danced across the garden.
    - /Time froze/, watching them sway.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar7
    narrationLines:
    - Until he forgot to care for his garden.
    - The roses slowly withered.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar8
    narrationLines:
    - The world colapsed, everything he built, falling apart.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar9a
    narrationLines:
    - He tried his best to regrow the garden, but it was already too late.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar9b
    narrationLines:
    - No matter how hard he tried, the flowers kept fading away.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar9c
    narrationLines:
    - There was nothing else he could do to save it.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar10
    narrationLines:
    - There was nothing left in that desolate space but the man and the girl.
    - The ruin of the garden had driven a quiet distance between them.
    - For one final time, he /desperately tried to mend the fragile earth/.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar11a
    narrationLines:
    - Yet, life would not return.
    - '"You''ve fought your battle. It is fine."'
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar11b
    narrationLines:
    - He surrendered to a heavy, breathless silence.
    - '"There is no need to despair..."'
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar11c
    narrationLines:
    - He gave up.
    - '"..."'
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar12
    narrationLines:
    - 'The girl gently approached him, '
    - wrapping him in a warm embrace, choosing to stay by his side.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar13
    narrationLines:
    - '"You are not alone..."'
    - Suddenly, a single, hopeful seed broke through the barren soil.
    - The man tenderly watered the earth, and the flower blossomed anew.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar14
    narrationLines:
    - As the girl drew near, the bloom turned a deep, vibrant red, standing stronger
      and more unyielding than ever before.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar15
    narrationLines:
    - Now, the man needed nothing more.
    - The flowers began to bloom endlessly on their own.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  - narrationId: nar16
    narrationLines:
    - '"A garden this breathtaking could never be grown by one heart alone," she
      whispered softly.'
    - '"It takes two souls to weave a paradise."'
    - From that moment on, they walked together. Wherever their footsteps fell, a
      beautiful garden flourished in their wake.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 10
  topCinematicBar: {fileID: 1220319693}
  bottomCinematicBar: {fileID: 663342298}
  narrationTextUI: {fileID: 1161394428}
  textCanvasGroup: {fileID: 1161394427}
  barSlideSpeed: 250
  typingSpeed: 0.05
  textFadeOutSpeed: 2
  typingSFX: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e43f9a9c01c543d40898d58b91fec3ce, type: 3}
